reviewText: I have seasons 1-3 and had to get four if you like the first 48 then you have to go get this series..

I enjoy crime documentaries.  It enlightens you to the how and why, people do what they do.  It also, shows the important role forensics plays in bringing perpetrators to justice.  Even crimes committed decades ago are now being solved through the use of forensics.  This series merely demonstrates that a sobbing woman can no longer convince a jury of justify homicide.

happy with this purchase,dvds were in good condition,the episodes included were entertaining, i cant complain,would purchase more seasons but i probably will watch it only once and forget about it as i did with this one.

I do have to say this season of Snapped was pretty interesting although the picture wasn't that clear but other than that if you like crime series trust me you'll want to add this to your collection.

I love this series and love the dvd collection. Nice, quick and quality packaging. A must have for "Snapped" fans!
